{
  "stem": "1581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, while we were marching, there was a guy who guarded us with a-- with a machine gun, and I tried to make conversation with him and ask him what happens to my wife and my child?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says-- he said, and I quote, don't worry, they are taken care of.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They come into a family lager, or a family camp, and they are much better off than you are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They will-- the women will go to work, but the children go to a children's home, and they're taken care of.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And don't worry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on you will be able to see them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what he told me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we later on finally came to the-- to the shower or the delousing station, whatever you want to call it, we spoke to the Polish prisoners.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, is that what he told you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't be a fool.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "See this chimney?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he pointed at this enormous symbol of Auschwitz which was visible from everywhere, where black smoke and flames came out all the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, that's where your, your child is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's where your wife is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And don't believe-- they were killed the moment you saw them part.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I listened to this, how could anybody with a sane mind believe such a fairy tale?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "How can any nation, particularly a nation like the German one-- cultured, mother of the most unbelievable poets, musicians and scientists-- how could they be bestial enough to kill a child because he's a child?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was just so unlikely, we just didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the seed of this horror was planted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And all the time there was in my mind, are they alive?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And will I see them again?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
